Class RangeMapper

java.lang.Object
  org.magelan.core.renderer.RangeMapper
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
PropertyRangeMapper
public abstract class RangeMapper
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

This abstract class provides a set of generic methods to map ranges of values to decoration objects. It is used to determine the proper decoration in accordance with a parameter of an element.

Version:
1.1, 02/2005
